What does Atlan crawl from Microsoft Power BI? | Atlan Documentation
Skip to main content
On this page
Atlan crawls and maps the following assets and properties from Microsoft Power BI.
Once you've
crawled Microsoft Power BI
, you can
use connector-specific filters
for quick asset discovery. The following filters are currently supported for these assets:
Measures
-  External measure filter
danger

reports
, Atlan also provides asset previews to help with quick discovery and give you the context you need.
